      <h1 class='title'>Child Poverty</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 08 June 2004 vol 422 c6WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_6ws' title='Col. 6WS &mdash; HC Deb 08 June 2004 vol 422 c6WS' name='column_6ws' href='#column_6ws' rel='bookmark'>6WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0422P2_20040608_CWS_6'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-andrew-smith' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0422P2_20040608_CWS_6' title='Link to this speech by Mr Andrew Smith' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-andrew-smith" title="Mr Andrew Smith">The Secretary of State for Work and Pensions (Mr. Andrew Smith)</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Today I have published the Government response to the Work and Pensions Committee Second Report of Session 2003&#x2013;04 [HC 85&#x2013;1] "Inquiry into Child Poverty in the UK" (CM 6200). Copies have been placed in the Library and are available for the Vote Office.</p><p>I am grateful to the Select Committee for their report which is detailed, comprehensive and helpful.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
